# Design System — Key Rules

Full reference in `DESIGN.md`. Product/brand context in `PRODUCT.md`.

## Hard Rules (never break)

1. No pure `#000` or `#fff` for large areas — use tinted tokens
2. No gradient text (`background-clip: text` + gradient)
3. No side-stripe borders (border-left/right > 1px as decorative accent)
4. No nested cards inside cards
5. Cap body line length at 65ch
6. Every interactive element needs hover, focus, active states (min 44×44px touch target)
7. Always respect `prefers-reduced-motion` on animations

## Color Token System

Brand palette uses OKLCH. Key semantic aliases:

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Primary CTA, headings | `midnight-indigo` = `--color-blue-800` |
| Page background | `background` = `--color-gray-50` |
| Body text | `foreground` = `--color-gray-800` |
| Muted text | `muted-foreground` = `--color-gray-700` |
| Card surface | `card` = white |
| Text on dark bg | `text-on-dark`, `text-on-dark-muted` |

Brand gradient (hero, footer): `brand-gradient` utility class.

**Never hardcode hex**. Use tokens from `src/styles/global.css @theme`.

## Typography

- Headings: `font-heading` (DM Serif Display)
- Body: `font-sans` (Outfit)
- Display heading: `text-[var(--text-display)]` = `clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem)`
- Headline: `text-[var(--text-headline)]` = `clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem)`

## CTA Buttons

```html
<!-- Primary -->
<a class="rounded-full bg-midnight-indigo text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-midnight-indigo-dark px-8 py-3">

<!-- Secondary (on dark bg) -->
<a class="rounded-full border-2 border-white/30 text-white hover:border-white/60 px-8 py-3">
```

## Cards

- `rounded-xl` + hairline border, flat at rest
- Hover: `hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md`
- No nested cards

## Motion

Easing: `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` (ease-out-quart). Durations: 150ms (fast), 250ms (base), 350ms (slow), 600ms (entrance).

Never animate layout properties (width, height, padding, margin).

## Elevation (shadows only on state change)

| State | Class |
|-------|-------|
| Card hover | `shadow-md` |
| Sticky/floating | `shadow-lg` |
| Hero/modal | `shadow-xl` |

## Spacing

Section rhythm: `py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-28`. Use `--space-section-*` and `--space-gap-*` tokens from global.css.

## Mobile CTA

`StickyBottomCTA.astro` is fixed at `bottom-0` on mobile (`md:hidden`). Main content needs `pb-20 md:pb-0` (already in BaseLayout `<main>`). Don't remove it.
